to see the authorized keys. (As the master needs to have the private key and the worker needs to have public key)
Now
ubuntu@ip-172-31-69-179:~/.ssh$ssh-keygen
You will be prompted with default file name, just keep pressing enter (3 times)

ubuntu@ip-172-31-69-179:~/.ssh$ls
